{
  "stem": "23626.6",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when the day of liberation, they actually opened the doors-- opened the gates between the women and men, and we gathered together.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, at the time, my sister's boyfriend introduced me to group of young men.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[BACKROUND NOISE] And one of them was my deceased husband, Joseph Jonas.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We only-- we were-- we were together in the factory.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But at night, we were separate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Men and women were separate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] [INAUDIBLE] And on the day of liberation, when they let us together, we actually-- I met those young fellows.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One of them was Joe, and others who I'm still friendly with now.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I found out later that Joe and others were-- had already formed a resistance group that Schindler was very alert to and knew about it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were connected with the Czechoslovakian people outside the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was told-- and that's not that long ago-- my husband really never spoke about it too much, because we didn't really exchange that much-- that he was really one that was bringing all the information from the Czech to the group.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they had a lot of arms, and Schindler knew about it and was helping them with it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There are other people now who speak about it more.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They know about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I just met, this Sunday, one of my friends who was very friendly with my-- with Joe-- with my deceased husband-- and he was telling me that he was a very important part of the resistance group in Brunnlitz.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He-- Victor Lewis.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he also was very active in the group.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was very impressed with him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a very [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] special person.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
